metadata.name: Valorien Genesis Pass #1
metadata.description:
If you are lucky to own one of these passes, congrats! Once our collection is sold out you will be automaticly airdropped one Valorien NFT from our original collection. 
 
 You will also get these benefits: 
 
 50% lifetime royalties of Valorien 
 
 10% of mint revenue from Valorien 
 
 Free airdrop of one Valorien NFT 
 
 Access to Valorien Genesis DAO
